data.whatILove: Ready for delivery with lots of upgrades!  Central location to all of Hampton Roads.  South Norfolk (SoNo) is an Historic Area located conveniently off I464 and within 8 minutes to Downtown Norfolk and Portsmouth.  Home is loaded with upgrades including hardwood floors, granite counter in kitchen, tile in master and first floor bath.  Home design features a first floor bedroom which is perfect for home office!  Busy job and life? Easy to maintain with minimal yard work and exterior upkeep.  HUGE master bedroom and large walk in closet.  Master bath features a double vanity, separate garden tub and separate shower.  Home has a unique built in storage room-large enough to hold motorcycle and lawn tools.  Ready for move in!  Builder will pay your closing cost.  Call  quick - only 1 left!  757 648-0999
